              <h3><b>STEM</b></h3>
              <p>Women tend to be largely under represented in STEM (science, technology, engineering, and math) fields.Because of the gender gap in STEM fields, there’s an effort to attract more women to STEM. Part of that effort is through college scholarships. If you’re planning to study STEM in college, check out the following links to learn about some of the best scholarships for women in STEM.</p>
              
              <ul >
                <li><a href="https://www.britishcouncil.org/study-work-abroad/in-uk/scholarship-women-stem">British Council scholarships</a></li>
