                <li><a href="https://www.iie.org/en/Programs/WeTech/STEM-Scholarships-for-Women/Juniper-Networks-Scholarship-and-Internship">Juniper Networks Scholarship</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.womentechmakers.com/">Women Techmakers Scholarship</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.gwis.org/page/fellowship_program">The Graduate Women In Science (GWIS) National Fellowships Program</a></li>
              </ul>
